Localization.Name: Deadhead Helmet Windfall
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Armor
Damage Reduction: 30%
Temp. Rating: -50 / 80 °C

Remind your enemies that death is coming with the Deadhead helmet. In place of a visor, the ghastly visage of a Human skull, lit from within by an infernal glow, is sure to send any opponent running.
